    " SGP4  the orbit propagator",
    " Beacon  sat's telemetry sig",
    "ORBITAL ELEMENTS",
    " Mean motion (n)  revs/day.",
    "  Period P = 1440 / n  (min)",
    " Semi-major axis a from n:",
    "  a = (mu / n^2)^(1/3),",
    "  n in rad/s, mu=398600 km3/s2",
    " Apogee  = a(1+e) - Re",
    " Perigee = a(1-e) - Re",
